$ v$logfile

This view can be queried to find the filenames, group numbers, log type (online or standby) and states of → development/databases/Oracle/architecture/database/files/online-redo-log-files[redo log files].


For example, to find all files of → development/databases/Oracle/architecture/database/files/online-redo-log-files/group[log group] 2, use
code {
select
  member
from
  v$logfile
where
  group# = 2
code }

sa:

  Compare with → development/databases/Oracle/installed/dynamic-performance-views/log

  → development/databases/Oracle/installed/dynamic-performance-views/[Oracle Dynamic Performance Views]
